node.text: and there is fault in that. We made ourselves sick. Our denial. Our division. Wear a mask, no. Cases and deaths sky rocket. Take the vaccine, waves of people do and the virus abates but then rebounds in the population that refuses to get it. Variants come and cases go again forcing more masking and the same people who refuse the vaccine, who refused the mask, refuse again.

node.text: that's where are again. Months of pleading that we need to protect ourselves with the gift of a vaccine or else...the variant will create cases at a rate we cant control, or else things may go back to being more restrictive, or else the fall may not be what we want it to be.  All this was said, all this was known. If you let the virus spread you will have more variants and more trouble and that's what happened. The science has not changed. The CDC stance and all the experts that come one all these shows...they have all been saying this.

node.text: please don't help make America sick again. We can't make ourselves sick again. We are all hearing about people getting sick. Heavy long lasting symptoms. Hospital. Even death. Again. This tale of two cities: the vaccinated and the vacuous. This deep denial is making us sick. Again.

node.text: please don't help make America sick again. We can't make ourselves sick again. We are all hearing about people getting sick. It is almost always the delta variant and we know the big factor - when they are vaccinated, you hear stories for the most part of a couple bad days but when they are not...it can be bad. Heavy long lasting symptoms. Hospital. Even death. Again. This tale of two cities: the vaccinated and the vacuous. This deep denial is making us sick. Again.
